headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Vehicles Discounts
content:
Players can get 30% off the Mobile Operations Center and its upgrades and Modifications. Plus, there is a range of vehicles on sale this week:

- Maibatsu Penumbra FF – 40% off
- Dinka Sugoi – 45% off
- Pfister 811 – 45% off
- Pfister Comet SR – 50% off

Head to the LS Car Meet to tune up your purchased vehicle or go to the Modding Bay of the Auto Shop.

And more! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
